'''Samona''' was the daughter of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] agents [[Harovan Toth]] and [[Tisha Rostek]], who met and fell in love on [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]] during the first days of the Rebel Alliance. Tisha Rostek died during the [[Battle of Thovinack]]. After that, Harovan Toth sent his daughter to the Rebel safeworld [[Isis/Legends|Isis]], to live with dissenters from Harovan's native planet [[Reynon]].<ref name="Journal 11">{{JournalCite|11|Cracken's Rebel Operatives (article)}}</ref>

